Eurostat Gross Value Added & Other Series by Industry

A dataset containing gross value added and other national statistics by industry for Eurostat countries.

data(GVAIndustry)

Format

A data frame with 136537 rows and 5 descriptive variables:

Country

European country, 34 total

Price

price metric, Real (base year 2010) or Nominal, should not be summed

Series

national accounts series, 9 total, use caution when summing

Industy

industry ISIC Rev.3.1, 21 top level industries

Year

year, 1996-2016, earlier & recent years may not be complete

Source

http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/data/database
